\c 28
\s Ahazi mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Ahazi akange ari wemakore makumi maviri pakutanga kwake kubata ushe; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore gumi namatanhatu; asi haana kuita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sababa vake Dhavhidhi;
\v 2 asi wakafamba nenzira dzamadzibaba aIsraeri, akaitira vaBhaariwo zvifananidzo zvendarira yakanyauswa.
\v 3 Uye akapisawo zvinonhuhwira pamupata womwanakomana waHinomi, akapisa vana vake mumoto, sezvainyangadza zvavahedheni, vakange vadzingwa naJehovha pamberi pavana vaIsraeri.
\v 4 Akabaira nokupisa zvinonhuhwira pamatunhu akakwirira, napazvikomo, napasi pemiti yese mitema.
\p
\v 5 Saka Jehovha Mwari wake akamuisa muruoko rwamambo weSiriya; vakamukunda, vakaenda navanhu vake vazhinji vakatapwa, vakanovaisa Dhamasiko. Naiye amene akaiswa muruoko rwamambo waIsraeri, akamukunda, akauraya vazhinji-zhinji.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti Peka mwanakomana waRemaria akauraya paJudha vanhu vane zvuru zvine zana namakumi maviri pazuva rimwe; vese vari varume voumhare; nokuti vakange vasiya Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo.
\v 7 Zikiri murume waEfuremu, akange ane simba, akauraya Maaseya mwanakomana wamambo, naAzirikami mutariri weimba, naErikana mukuru kutevera mambo.
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakatapa pakati pehama dzavo vanhu vane zvuru zvina mazana maviri, vakadzi, vanakomana, navanasikana, vakapambawo zvizhinji kwavari; vakanoisa Samaria izvo zvakapambiwa.
\v 9 Asi kwakange kuno muporofita waJehovha, wainzi Obhedhi; iye akaenda kundosangana nehondo yakange youya Samaria, akati kwavari: Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba enyu akange atsamwira vaJudha, saka akavaisa mumaoko enyu, makavauraya nehasha dzakasvikira kudenga.
\v 10 Zvino munoti muchamanikidza vana vaJudha naveJerusarema, vave vatapwa venyu varanda navarandakadzi; ko imwi hamune mhosvawo momene pamberi paJehovha Mwari wenyu here?
\v 11 Naizvozvo zvino chindinzwai, mudzose vatapwa vamakatapa pakati pehama dzenyu; nokuti Jehovha akutsamwirai kwazvo.
\v 12 Ipapo vamwe vakuru vavana vaEfuremu, vaiti: Azaria mwanakomana waJohwanani, naBherekia mwanakomana waMeshiremoti, naJehizikia mwanakomana waSharumi, naAmasa mwanakomana waHadhirai, vakadzivisa avo vabva pakurwa,
\v 13 vakati kwavari: Hamungapindi pano navatapwa, nokuti munovavarira kuita chinhu chichatiparisa mhaka pana Jehovha, mugowedzera pazvivi zvedu nemhosva yedu; nokuti mhosva yedu ihuru, VaIsraeri vatsamwirwa kwazvo naJehovha.
\v 14 Ipapo varwi vakasiya vatapwa nezvakapambiwa kumachinda neungano yese.
\v 15 Zvino ava varume varehwa mazita avo, vakasimuka, vakatora vatapwa, vakafukidza vese vakange vakashama pakati pavo nezvakapambiwa, vakavapfekedza nokuvaisa shangu, ndokuvapa zvokudya nezvokumwa, vakavazodza, vakatasvisa vese vakange vasine simba pambongoro, vakavaisa Jeriko, guta remichindwe, kuhama dzavo; ipapo vakadzokera Samaria.
\p
\v 16 Panguva iyo mambo Ahazi akatuma shoko kumadzibaba aAsiriya, kuti vamubatsire.
\v 17 Nokuti VaEdhomu vakange vasvikazve, vakakunda vaJudha vakatapa vatapwa.
\v 18 NaVaFirisitiawo vakange vavamba maguta amapani, naaiva kurutivi rwechamhembe rwaJudha, vakakunda Bheti-Shemeshi, neAjaroni, neGedheroti, neSoko, nemisha yawo, neTimina, nemisha yaro, neGimizo nemisha yaro; vakagarapo.
\v 19 Nokuti Jehovha akaninipisa vaJudha nokuda kwaAhazi mambo waIsraeri; nokuti akange aita zvakaipa paJudha, akatadzira Jehovha kwazvo.
\v 20 Zvino Tirigatipirineseri mambo weAsiriya akauya kuzorwa naye, akamumanikidza, asi haana kumukunda.
\v 21 Nokuti Ahazi akatora mugove wefuma paimba yaJehovha, napaimba yamambo, neyamachinda, akazvipa mambo weAsiriya; asi hazvina kumubatsira.
\p
\v 22 Asi panguva yokutambudzika kwake, akanyanya kutadzira Jehovha, iye mambo Ahazi.
\v 23 Nokuti akabaira vamwari veDhamasiko, vakange vamukunda, akati: Vamwari vamadzimambo Asiriya zvavanovabatsira, ini ndichavabayirawo, kuti vandibatsirewo. Asi ivo vakamuparadza iye naVaIsraeri vese pamwe chete naye.
\v 24 Zvino Ahazi akaunganidza midziyo yeimba yaMwari akaputsanya midziyo yeimba yaMwari, akapfiga mikova yeimba yaJehovha; akazviitira aritari pese-pese paJerusarema.
\v 25 Akaitawo matunhu akakwirira paguta rimwe nerimwe raJudha kuzopisira vamwe vamwari zvinonhuhwira ipapo, akatsamwisa Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba ake.
\p
\v 26 Zvino mamwe mabasa ake, netsika dzake dzese, dzokutanga nedzokupedzisira, tarirai zvakanyorwa mubhuku yamadzimambo aJudha naIsraeri.
\v 27 Ahazi akarara namadzibaba ake, vakamuviga muguta, imo muJerusarema; nokuti havana kumuisa pamarinda amadzimambo aIsraeri; Hezekia mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.